Internal CSS in html:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
body {background-color: powderblue;}
h1   {color: blue;}
p    {color: red;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Welcome to My website</h1>
<p>How can i help you?</p>

</body>
</html>

External CSS in html:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<h1>Hello</h1>
<p>How can i help you?</p>

</body>
</html>

